    {
      "id": "3c48dd29-0b3d-4d16-8dcf-8854297235a2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors also use an attention mechanism to obtain better representations of student behavior. Results on 3 datasets show that approach is better at predicting student outcomes for all student subgroups.",
